values: so i went to Dennys tonight and hungout with Josh, Brett, Nick and Sheldon, it was so amazing, ive missed my boys for so long and im now an Albertan its strange eh, you tell eachother we'll always be friends and together but im in Edmonton and Josh is in...Red Deer i think it is, its funny how we all grow up, but the thing is that im now the one who has left them, and that picture has now faded another person out...there are now 3 left out of 12 of us...its sad to see but i was happy to hear that they'll be moving with Josh in Sept so i wont totally lose them ill just be further away haha, and i think Josh and I will be becoming closer friends cause he wants to start comming to New City with me, btw thats a Punk/Goth bar in Edmonton, its alot of fun there..well later days for now

hmm well over a month and i have nothing new to report, wow how awesome am i. well i havent been doin anything really just sittin at home, and driving around yeah go me, driving all by my lonesome self, hahaha i dont even get a co-pilot woot woot. meh its all fun though.

well this is it...this will be my last update before i move...and are there alot of things i wish i could have done out here...no ive lived my life as best as possible...are there things i wish i could have said to people, for sure, are there people ill miss...well everyone that i was happy enough to call a friend, how many regrets do i have 1..my only regret was i didnt let people know exactly how i feel....im gunna miss this city...and all my friends out here, it was a great life out here guys...i love you all...and if ive said anything to upset you...calling you not my friend...and telling you i dont wanna talk to you ever again(i think you know who im talking about) forget those words...

booyah guess who is moving out on his own...well me no shit, and when well im moving in less than a month, i honestly cant stand westsyde anymore, cause well iunno why but Sheldon just up and stopped talking to me, sumtin says its because i actually hangout with older ppl cause that kid is easily intimidated that i wouldnt be surprised thats why..hahahah i love how many people dont like me cause well honestly they can go fuck themselves

wow who's been a busy fucker...yeah me thats who...but i love it...you know that thing called maturing...yeah guess who did it, yeah me again. But its weird with me maturing i dont even hangout with the same people anymore which i guess is a bad thing but i dont feel bad for it at all, im almost happier now, cuz a few of them dont realize that it is time to grow up and start hanging out with people your own age, dont get me wrong i love my younger friends...i just iunno its hard to explain, and well yeah is it bad when you like sumone almost 5 years older than you and who is in a longterm relationship? yeah i thought it was, but i also got sumtin inside me saying go and see if it would work with my one friend who ive known for a real long time....well thats the next chapter in my life written

so, how do i start....I HATE MY FRIENDS....well atleast a couple of them, because oh no...im hanging out with people older than me that makes me an asshole...im sorry im going to hangout with other adults...and fuck its Dean and Tamara...i love those guys, and Sheldon hates hanging out with me now i swear because i hangout with James and Charlie...they are such fucking cool people, and hes all uncomfterble around them...i can understand why he only hangsout with younger people, he cant handle adult situations...fuck them

so your feeling unimportant, cause uv got nothing to say....so yeah hey who is gunna hangout with me on my day off tomorrow, cause i miss Laura, hahaha she and i should do whippets again lmao...so fuun...and well for things i dont like talking about other Laura...well....iunno im kinda happy i havent seen her for 4 days...who knows maybe i should stop hanging out with her.

so today is my day off work WOOT WOOT! and i sure have nothing to do...well i hope Sheldoom calls me cause it sure is international go to Dennys day, well thats what i call it. but yeah we sure hafta go to it tonight, so for some fucking reason i had a dream about Megan last night...man i hadnt had one for like 5 days..haha its funny cause i have one after this whole Laura thing happend hmm i actually wonder if its a coinsidence?....meh who cares i sure as hell dont, so i decided that im gunna hate the world again, i hate being a nice guy...i want to be an asshole...it was easier on me..my life blew ass when i was trying to be nice again, i had to do all this..o0o i care bullshit...fuckit i dont, i care about me myself and i..ill only go to Dennys...no more social hangouts..ill just sit in my room and play Mercenaries...cuz i rule at that game..so thats all for now

hahahaha so i got my call back today...and well i told Laura that i wanted to kiss her hahaha hey it was true...just i didnt say all of it...right lmao...well guys i gotta go catch my bus...btw whoever lives in Kamloops DENNYS NIGHT! all come...we hafta keep tradition goin...Dennys night is a go
haha if u could only know what i was think at Dennys tonight Laura...*sigh* only if u were into it...

well im goin to Penticton in...1 hour...and man o man...im gunna miss my Laura's i tell you what. but meh yah know its not like im not commin back...im just looking for work :) but when i do go for good im gunna give them both HUGE hugs...cuz ill miss them that much, and its not like im not gunna see them ever...they are the only people id come back to visit...and they can come down, but *sigh* lil Laura...jeez...man...shes amazing...i think i like her ....shhh...dont tell, an Laura...other..one....oh my god she is soo funny its not even....funny?....yeah, she is alot of fun to hangout with...ill miss them for this week or so im gone..

oh well.....god it sux to be a good guy...i get taken advantage of...like honestly every1 thinks im a jerk, its cause you gotta be to make it in this world...im a real nice guy, but im not allowed to, life is cut throat, its cut or be cut, its the whole, nice guys finish last...well its true, and so i became a little cold and my heart is warm(metaphorically) and ppl cant know...cuz ill be hurt  then...maybe now all of you ppl wont judge me so fast...besides you dont know why i did what i did....matt you an i talked about it, the only convo we had...

well Emilie, Matt and I all talked today...it went awesome, like we were all very polite, there was no arguing involved...it was beautiful, lol...but yeah...nothing has changed and since Matt was a real jerk to me, hinting at me being an ass to Emilie, even if he tries to deny it...but nothing has changd i still want her, i still want to be with her, and im gunna try to be with her, no matter what, im gunna see if Lindsay will let me live with her until I can find a job and a place to live...she WILL be mine....I hope at least...but we'll see eh...oh well WHATEVER!, IM HAVING A PAAAARTAY ALL BY MYSELF, lmao....man o'man im gettin hyper...lol, we'll see what happens ttyl gunna continue watching the movie

well  this weekend was an interesting one...brett and me went to Penticton so i could go see Melinda...well i regret that, cause now she hates me, i dont know what i said wrong..i told her that i felt ignored when we were hanging out...cause i was, she was all friendly with brett, and she barely said a word to me...well who cares, i might as well cut now and let everybody realize what they lost...but i NEVER would do that to Emilie..I love her way to much, and thats the scary thing, it isnt a friendship love anymore...its getting to be more than that, and im scared...cause everybody is gunna hate me...shes 14 and im 18 goin on 19, when she is 18 ill be 22, but what do i care, that is the only problem, and it aint a problem, cause i dont care about age...well Emilie is back so im gunna chat wit her...

well last night was an eventful evening...brett and I decided that the rain was a beautiful thing...and he never really has gotten his truck muddy yet, well if you call what dipshit sheldon did gettin it muddy then...but yeah, we were mud-boggin for an hour straight and now the truck is fuckin beautiful...globs of mud hangin off, and all:p, yeah, and the best part was that we ad our windows rolled down so when we were goin sideways in the pit, mud was flying in the window and i got covered in mud as well lmao, it was BEAUTIFUL!, oh man it was some dope ass shit yo....but yeah, im gunna go now, ttyl...Emilie isnt home yet *tear*, but oh well, later dayz
